em at the end of the races as many times as I could,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"the national anthem\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"many times\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In sharp contrast to Ledecky's runaway win in the 1,500m the 800m freestyle was a thriller from start to finish, with Ariarne Titmus matching her stroke-for-stroke for almost the entire distance.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sharp contrast\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky's runaway win\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500m\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m freestyle\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"a thriller\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"start\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"her stroke\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"stroke\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"almost the entire distance\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with the American setting a relentless, grinding pace her great Australian rival would never get her nose in front settling for silver with Ledecky getting to the wall first in a time of 8 minutes, 11.04 seco